{"article_id":"vHgjuzCYlhJcyt6c","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Three months into the new Congress ,","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"some Republicans are fearful","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"that their failure","depth":10},{"id":3,"text":"to repeal ObamaCare","depth":10},{"id":4,"text":"could spell doom for the rest of President Trump ' s legislative agenda .","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"Some Capitol Hill Republicans have envisioned the nightmare scenario for 2017 ,","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"and it goes like this :","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"No ObamaCare repeal .","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"No tax reform .","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"No trillion-dollar infrastructure package .","depth":11},{"id":10,"text":"No border wall .","depth":11},{"id":11,"text":"It ' s a striking change from the period after Election Day ,","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"when GOP leaders vowed","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"that the new unified Republican government would \" go big ,","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"go bold \"","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"and deliver for the American people .","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"While many Republicans hold out hope","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"the ObamaCare repeal bill will be revived ,","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"skeptics say","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"the GOP infighting during last month ' s healthcare collapse may have poisoned the well for future big-ticket legislative deals .","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"\" I don ' t see how you put a coalition together","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"to deal with tax reform , \"","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"said one House Republican","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"who is close to Speaker Paul Ryan","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"Paul Davis Ryan Retirees should say 'no thanks ' to Romney 's Social Security plan","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"California Governor Newsom and family dress as 2020 Democrats for Halloween DC 's liaison to rock ' n ' roll MORE","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"( R-Wis. )","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"and his leadership team .","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"\" Unless we can bridge this divide","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"and get a win on the board ,","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"I don ' t know","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"how we pull the other things together , all the other big things","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"we got ta do . \"","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"Despite some signs of life ,","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"healthcare talks between the White House and centrist and conservative holdouts did not result in a deal","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"before Congress began a two-week April recess .","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"And the recriminations among Republicans only seem to be getting nastier .","depth":6},{"id":37,"text":"Rep. Mark Meadows","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"( R-N.C. ) ,","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"the head of the conservative House Freedom Caucus , \" is a pathological liar","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"who isn ' t interested in getting to yes , \"","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"one House GOP colleague of Meadows told in a fit of frustration over the stalled health negotiations .","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"But Rep. Raúl Labrador","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"( R-Idaho ) ,","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"a fellow Freedom Caucus leader , defended Meadows as \" a man of great integrity. \"","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"\" When members of Congress resort to personal attacks","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"while hiding behind anonymity , \"","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"Labrador said ,","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"\" it ' s usually because their position is weak in the first place","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"and they are getting heat back home","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"for not keeping the promises","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"that they made to their constituents . \"","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"At a town hall in Cedar Springs , Mich. , GOP Rep. Justin Amash Justin AmashTrump allies assail impeachment on process","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"while House Democrats promise open hearings soon","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"Hoyer :","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"We are going to move as fast","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"'","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"as the facts and truth dictate ' on open hearings","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"Conway spars with Wallace on whether White House will cooperate with impeachment inquiry after formal vote","depth":6},{"id":59,"text":"MORE , another Meadows ally , hurled blame at the feet of Ryan :","depth":6},{"id":60,"text":"Republicans need \" either a change in direction from this Speaker ,","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"or we need a new Speaker . \"","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"\" I don ' t know","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"that the Lord himself could unite our caucus , \"","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"veteran Rep. Mike Simpson","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"( R-Idaho )","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"told The Associated Press .","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"Late last month ,","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"when Ryan realized","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"he was short of the votes","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"and yanked the health insurance bill off the floor ,","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"he and Trump insisted","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"they were moving on to tax reform .","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"But within days , they had returned to the healthcare legislation .","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"In part , it ' s because passing the ObamaCare repeal-and replace-bill smooths the path for tax reform , something","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"Ryan and many other congressional leaders have emphasized to members .","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"Mick Mulvaney , Trump ' s budget director and a top health negotiator , has been explicit about the need","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"to pass a health bill ,","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"telling RealClearPolitics","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"it ' s the \" linchpin \" of Trump ' s entire legislative agenda .","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"The bill ,","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"known as the American Health Care Act ,","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"would cut about $ 1 trillion in ObamaCare taxes over a decade ,","depth":7},{"id":83,"text":"significantly lowering the revenue budget baseline .","depth":6},{"id":84,"text":"That improved baseline would give Republicans greater flexibility","depth":6},{"id":85,"text":"to lower corporate tax rates in comprehensive tax reform .","depth":6},{"id":86,"text":"Some Republicans ,","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"including Rep. Tom Reed","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"( N.Y. ) ,","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"have also echoed Trump ' s call","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"for tax reform and infrastructure to be tied together .","depth":7},{"id":91,"text":"\" These items are all connected ,","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"and the connectivity is funding , \"","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"Rep. Daniel Webster","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"( R-Fla. ) ,","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"a critic of the GOP healthcare bill , told .","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"Anti-tax crusader Grover Norquist highlighted the challenges","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"facing GOP leaders since the delay of the healthcare bill .","depth":7},{"id":98,"text":"\" You try to run a marathon ,","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"but","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"if you don ' t do healthcare first ,","depth":12},{"id":101,"text":"you ' re a trillion dollars back from the start of the marathon , \"","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"Norquist said during a recent visit to ' s offices .","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"Without healthcare , \" it ' s an extra 10 to 20 miles","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"to get the trillion dollars ,","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"and then you ' re off to the races .","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"\" Taking a trillion dollars of tax increases off the table gets you closer to what you wanted tax reform to look like . \"","depth":7},{"id":107,"text":"Ryan has argued","depth":7},{"id":108,"text":"that tax reform will be an easier lift than healthcare","depth":8},{"id":109,"text":"because Republicans are more unified around the idea","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"of fixing the outdated U.S. tax code .","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"But even some of Ryan ' s closest allies in Congress dispute his assessment .","depth":8},{"id":112,"text":"\" I have a lot of respect for the Speaker ,","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"but I don ' t see it that way , \"","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"longtime Rep. Tom Cole","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"( R-Okla. ) ,","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"a senior appropriator , said in a phone interview .","depth":10},{"id":117,"text":"\" There is a lot of resistance \" to Ryan ' s proposal","depth":8},{"id":118,"text":"known as the border-adjustment plan ,","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"which would impose a 20 percent tax on imports .","depth":9},{"id":120,"text":"The idea , as of now , is for Republicans to tackle tax reform","depth":9},{"id":121,"text":"using the budget reconciliation process ,","depth":9},{"id":122,"text":"which would allow them to avoid mustering 60 votes","depth":9},{"id":123,"text":"to break a filibuster .","depth":9},{"id":124,"text":"But Cole argued","depth":10},{"id":125,"text":"that that process imposes constraints","depth":12},{"id":126,"text":"- specifically , a bill","depth":14},{"id":127,"text":"passed under reconciliation","depth":14},{"id":128,"text":"can not hike the budget deficit after 10 years -","depth":13},{"id":129,"text":"and could lead to the same intraparty warfare","depth":12},{"id":130,"text":"that thwarted the ObamaCare repeal bill .","depth":12},{"id":131,"text":"\" Since we weren ' t able to do healthcare reform by reconciliation ,","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"why would we be able to do tax reform by reconciliation ?","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"It ' s really difficult , \"","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"said Cole ,","depth":12},{"id":135,"text":"who added","depth":13},{"id":136,"text":"that Republicans should focus on more basic government functions .","depth":13},{"id":137,"text":"\" We can still get some things done , \"","depth":10},{"id":138,"text":"he said ,","depth":10},{"id":139,"text":"\" but we need to get the government funded ,","depth":10},{"id":140,"text":"think about how to deal with the debt ceiling","depth":11},{"id":141,"text":"and begin negotiations \" on fiscal 2018 appropriation bills .","depth":11},{"id":142,"text":"It ' s no secret how much Ryan despises stopgap or catch-all omnibus spending bills ,","depth":8},{"id":143,"text":"but the former Budget Committee chairman will have to shepherd one through the House anyway at the end of the month .","depth":8},{"id":144,"text":"Lawmakers need to pass a spending bill by April 28","depth":9},{"id":145,"text":"to avert a government shutdown .","depth":9},{"id":146,"text":"They ' ll have just three full legislative days","depth":10},{"id":147,"text":"to act ,","depth":10},{"id":148,"text":"given that the House isn ' t scheduled to return from its recess until April 25 .","depth":9},{"id":149,"text":"Trump is getting impatient with all the congressional inaction ,","depth":4},{"id":150,"text":"especially as his administration nears the 100-day mark .","depth":4},{"id":151,"text":"He won a major victory with the Senate ' s confirmation of his Supreme Court pick , Neil Gorsuch .","depth":5},{"id":152,"text":"But now he wants Congress to pass funding for his wall along the southern border , one of his central campaign promises .","depth":5},{"id":153,"text":"GOP leaders and their allies say","depth":6},{"id":154,"text":"the government funding bill is the wrong place","depth":7},{"id":155,"text":"to have a fight over the wall .","depth":7},{"id":156,"text":"\" What ' s the justification","depth":7},{"id":157,"text":"for shutting down the government","depth":9},{"id":158,"text":"that you run ? \"","depth":9},{"id":159,"text":"asked Cole , the chairman of an appropriations subcommittee .","depth":8},{"id":160,"text":"\" It ' d be a Republican House and Senate","depth":8},{"id":161,"text":"shutting down a Republican administration .","depth":8},{"id":162,"text":"That doesn ' t make any sense to me . \"","depth":7},{"id":163,"text":"Healthcare talks have continued into the two-week recess .","depth":5},{"id":164,"text":"Vice President Pence has been calling up House negotiators and conservative outside groups","depth":7},{"id":165,"text":"as he searches for a deal ,","depth":7},{"id":166,"text":"GOP sources said .","depth":6},{"id":167,"text":"\" I still feel confident","depth":7},{"id":168,"text":"that we still will be able to move forward with our plan .","depth":7},{"id":169,"text":"The American people deserve it","depth":9},{"id":170,"text":"and they want it ,","depth":9},{"id":171,"text":"and we ' re certainly committed to it , \"","depth":8},{"id":172,"text":"Rep. Vicky Hartzler","depth":9},{"id":173,"text":"( R-Mo . )","depth":9},{"id":174,"text":"told .","depth":8},{"id":175,"text":"\" Where there is a will ,","depth":7},{"id":176,"text":"there is a way ,","depth":7},{"id":177,"text":"and certainly there is a lot of will here","depth":7},{"id":178,"text":"to get this done . \"","depth":7},{"id":179,"text":"But","depth":4},{"id":180,"text":"without a healthcare victory","depth":6},{"id":181,"text":"to tout back home in western Missouri ,","depth":6},{"id":182,"text":"Hartzler said","depth":6},{"id":183,"text":"she planned to spend the recess","depth":7},{"id":184,"text":"taking her anti-opioid campaign to local high schools .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":369,"left":333,"right":368,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":333,"left":251,"right":332,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":251,"left":217,"right":250,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":217,"left":200,"right":216,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":200,"left":195,"right":199,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":195,"left":189,"right":194,"relation":"e